                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18450818-1658-offence-1 t18450818-name-497"></join>James Case</persName>, and cutting and wounding him in and upon his right arm, on the <rs id="t18450818-cd-27" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18450818-1658-offence-1 t18450818-cd-27"></join>15th of July</rs>, at <placeName id="t18450818-geo-5">
                        <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18450818-1658-offence-1 t18450818-geo-5"></join>St. Luke</placeName>, with intent to do him some grievous bodily harm.</rs>
